
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Consumidor as Consumidore/Aplicación
    participant API as API Depósito Cheque <br> Epica 2267: PagoPrestamo <br> HU 57109:  POST - /payments/payment-execution-transfer/v1/initiate-loan-payment
    participant CL as Caché Local
    participant Lambda as Lambda de parámetros
    participant Lib as Librería Pipeline (ConfigMap)
    participant Idempotencia as Componente de Idempotencia <br> POST: integrity-handler/v1/idempotency/generate
    participant wrappergt as Wrapper Abanks Guatemala <br/> SP: OSB_P_PAGO_PRESTAMO 
    participant wrapperpa as Wrapper Abanks Panamá <br/> SP: OSB_P_PAGO_PRESTAMO 
    participant wrappercts as Wrapper CTS Cobis <br/> OP: OpPagarPrestamo 
    participant event as AWS EventBridge <br> Componente de Idempotencia 
    participant Errors as Control de Errores <br> <<Librería de mapeo de errores>>
    
    Note over Consumidor, Errors: Flujos Guatemaña, Nicaragua y Panamá (GT01 | NI01 | PA01) - Pago préstamo

    Consumidor->>API: REST Request
    Note right of Consumidor: body: <br> paymentAmount, <br> loanId, <br> debitAccountReference, <br> currencyCode, <br> branchReference, <br> serviceReference, <br> interfaceReferenceNumber, <br> consumerIPAddress

    API->>API: Validar Request
    Note over API: Valida campos obligatorios según contrato OpenAPI 

    API->>API: Validación exitosa

    alt Consulta parametros en caché local

        API->>CL: Consultar parámetros Lambda Parámetros caché local
        Note right of API: Domain: "PAYMENT_EXECUTION_TRANSFER" <br> name: "INITIATE_LOAN_PAYMENT" <br> country: XRS 

        CL->>API: Obtiene parámetros Lambda Parámetros Cahé Local
        Note left of CL: Obtiene parámetros de regionalización y negocio
 
    else Consulta  parametros en Lambda Parámetros / Parameter Store

        API->>Lambda: Consultar parámetros lambda parámetros
        Note right of API: Domain: "PAYMENT_EXECUTION_TRANSFER" <br> name: "INITIATE_LOAN_PAYMENT" <br> country: XRS 

        Lambda->>API: Obtiene parámetros Lambda Parámetros
        Note left of Lambda: Obtiene parámetros de regionalización y negocio

        API->>CL: Guarda parámetros lambda Parámetros en caché local
        Note right of API: value.param-name 

    end

    API->>API: Validar Servicio Regional
    Note over API: Usando parámetros de regionalización obtenidos

    API->>API: Validación Regional success
    Note over API: Servicio habilitado para GT01 | PA01 | NI01 

    API->>API: Aplica Patrón Strategy
    Note over API: Implementa lógica según el país (header.sourceBank)

    alt header.sourceBank == GT01 

        API->>Lib: Consulta Constantes
    
        Lib->>API: Retorna constantes necesarias
        Note left of Lib: Constantes: <br> connectionTypeGT <br> operationTypeGT <br> catalogueNameGT  <br> procedureNameGT <br> caller-service 

        API->>Idempotencia: Consume API Idempotencia 
        Note right of API: Mapeo de Campos: <br> Correlation-Id: header.Correlation-Id <br> Caller-Service: const.caller-service <br> "methodVersion": "1.0" <br> dataPayload: {request}

        Idempotencia->>API: Response API Idempotencia 
        Note left of Idempotencia: Response: data {status, code, tittle, detail, correlation-id}

        API->>API: Evalua response API Idempotencia

        alt If If data.code != 0

            API->> Errors: Mapear código de error

            Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado

            API->> Consumidor: Retorna error
            Note left of API: HTTP 422: Transacción efectuada previamente

        else If If data.code == 0

            API->>API: Construye Request Wrapper Proxy Abanks GT - SP: OSB_P_PAGO_PRESTAMO
            Note over API: Mapeo: <br> header:  caller-service = const.caller-service <br> body: <br> connectionType = const.connectionTypeGT <br> operationType = const.operationTypeGT <br> catalogueName = const.catalogueNameGT <br> procedureName = const.procedureNameGT <br> params { <br> LOAN_NUMBER = request.loanID <br> PAYMENT_AMOUNT = request.paymentAmount <br> DEBIT_ACCOUNT = request.debitAccountReference <br> INTERFACE_REFERENCE_NO = request.interfaceReferenceNumber <br> USERNAME = header.application-user <br> }

            API->>wrappergt: Consume Wrapper Proxy Abanks GT - SP: OSB_P_PAGO_PRESTAMO
            Note right of API: header: caller-service <br> body: <br> connectionType, operationType, catalogueName, procedureName, params

            wrappergt->>API: Response Wrapper Proxy Abanks GT - SP: OSB_P_PAGO_PRESTAMO
            Note over wrappergt: Response: <br> success, data

            API->>API: Evalúa Response Wrapper Proxy Abanks GT - SP: OSB_P_PAGO_PRESTAMO

            alt If success == true 

                API->>API: Construye response API
                Note over API: Mapeo: <br> transactionDateTime = DATE_TIME <br> loanId = request.loanId <br> installmentReference = DUE_ID <br> transactionReference = TRANSACTION_ID <br> valueDate = VALUEDATE <br> paymentAmount = request.paymentAmount

                API->>event: Envía envento al eventBridge API Idempotencia 
                Note right of API: Mensaje: <br> Correlation-Id: header.Correlation-Id <br> Caller-Service: lambda.caller-service <br> detail-type: "provider.response" <br> request: {request} <br> Transaccion: success 

                API->>Consumidor: Response Exitoso
                Note left of API: HTTP 200: Response Body 

            else If success != false 

                API->>event: Envía envento al eventBridge API Idempotencia 
                Note right of API: Mensaje: <br> Correlation-Id: header.Correlation-Id <br> Caller-Service: lambda.caller-service <br> detail-type: "provider.response" <br> request: {request} <br> Transaccion: TimeOut

                API->> Errors: Mapear código de error

                Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado

                API->> Consumidor: Retorna error
                Note left of API: HTTP 422 + Wrapper.mensajeError

            end
        
        end

    end

    alt header.sourceBank == PA01

        API->>Lib: Consulta Constantes
    
        Lib->>API: Retorna constantes necesarias
        Note left of Lib: Constantes: <br> connectionTypePA <br> operationTypePA <br> catalogueNamePA  <br> procedureNamePA <br> caller-service 

        API->>Idempotencia: Consume API Idempotencia 
        Note right of API: Mapeo de Campos: <br> Correlation-Id: header.Correlation-Id <br> Caller-Service: const.caller-service <br> "methodVersion": "1.0" <br> dataPayload: {request}

        Idempotencia->>API: Response API Idempotencia 
        Note left of Idempotencia: Response: data {status, code, tittle, detail, correlation-id}

        API->>API: Evalua response API Idempotencia

        alt If If data.code != 0

            API->> Errors: Mapear código de error

            Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado

            API->> Consumidor: Retorna error
            Note left of API: HTTP 422: Transacción efectuada previamente

        else If If data.code == 0

            API->>API: Construye Request Wrapper Proxy Abanks PA - SP: OSB_P_PAGO_PRESTAMO
            Note over API: Mapeo: <br> header:  caller-service = const.caller-service <br> body: <br> connectionType = const.connectionTypePA <br> operationType = const.operationTypePA <br> catalogueName = const.catalogueNamePA <br> procedureName = const.procedureNamePA <br> params { <br> LOAN_NUMBER = request.loanID <br> PAYMENT_AMOUNT = request.paymentAmount <br> DEBIT_ACCOUNT = request.debitAccountReference <br> INTERFACE_REFERENCE_NO = request.interfaceReferenceNumber <br> USERNAME = header.application-user <br>}

            API->>wrapperpa: Consume Wrapper Proxy Abanks PA - SP: OSB_P_PAGO_PRESTAMO
            Note right of API: header: caller-service <br> body: <br> connectionType, operationType, catalogueName, procedureName, params

            wrapperpa->>API: Response Wrapper Proxy Abanks PA - SP: OSB_P_PAGO_PRESTAMO
            Note over wrapperpa: Response: <br> success, data

            API->>API: Evalúa Response Wrapper Proxy Abanks PA - SP: OSB_P_PAGO_PRESTAMO

            alt If success == true 

                API->>API: Construye response API
                Note over API: Mapeo: <br> transactionDateTime = DATE_TIME <br> loanId = request.loanId <br> installmentReference = DUE_ID <br> transactionReference = TRANSACTION_ID <br> valueDate = VALUEDATE <br> paymentAmount = request.paymentAmount

                API->>event: Envía envento al eventBridge API Idempotencia 
                Note right of API: Mensaje: <br> Correlation-Id: header.Correlation-Id <br> Caller-Service: lambda.caller-service <br> detail-type: "provider.response" <br> request: {request} <br> Transaccion: success 

                API->>Consumidor: Response Exitoso
                Note left of API: HTTP 200: Response Body 

            else If success != false 

                API->>event: Envía envento al eventBridge API Idempotencia 
                Note right of API: Mensaje: <br> Correlation-Id: header.Correlation-Id <br> Caller-Service: lambda.caller-service <br> detail-type: "provider.response" <br> request: {request} <br> Transaccion: TimeOut

                API->> Errors: Mapear código de error

                Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado

                API->> Consumidor: Retorna error
                Note left of API: HTTP 422 + Wrapper.mensajeError

            end
        
        end

    end

    alt header.sourceBank == NI01

        API->>Lib: Consulta Constantes
    
        Lib->>API: Retorna constantes necesarias
        Note left of Lib: Constantes: <br> operationNameNI  <br> caller-service

        API->>Idempotencia: Consume API Idempotencia 
        Note right of API: Mapeo de Campos: <br> Correlation-Id: header.Correlation-Id <br> Caller-Service: const.caller-service <br> "methodVersion": "1.0" <br> dataPayload: {request}

        Idempotencia->>API: Response API Idempotencia 
        Note left of Idempotencia: Response: 

        API->>API: Evalua response API Idempotencia

        alt If If data.code != 0

            API->> Errors: Mapear código de error

            Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado

            API->> Consumidor: Retorna error
            Note left of API: HTTP 422: Transacción efectuada previamente

        else If If data.code == 0

            API->>API: Construye Request Wrapper CTS Cobis - OP: OpPagarPrestamo
            Note over API: Mapeo: <br> body: <br> operation = const.operationNI <br> flagcache = false <br> payload [ <br> { type = "contextoTransaccional" <br> identificadorTransaccional, = request.interfaceReferenceNumber <br> codCanalOriginador = header.Channel <br> ipConsumidor = request.consumerIPAddress } <br> { type = transaccion, <br> valMonto = request.paymentAmount } <br> { type = "prestamo", <br> producto.valNumeroProducto = request.loanId } <br> { type = "cuenta", <br> codCuentaHabiente = debitAccountReference } <br> { type = oficina, <br> codOficina = request.branchReference } <br> { type = "moneda", <br> multimoneda = request.currencyCode } <br> { type = "canal", <br> servicio = request.serviceReference } ] 
            
            API->>wrappercts: Consume Wrapper CTS Cobis - OP: OpPagarPrestamo
            Note right of API: body: <br> operation, flagcache, payload

            wrappercts->>API: Response Wrapper CTS Cobis - OP: OpPagarPrestamo
            Note over wrappercts: Response: <br> success, data

            API->>API: Evalúa Response Wrapper CTS Cobis - OP: OpPagarPrestamo

            alt If success == true 

                API->>API: Construye response API
                Note over API: Mapeo: <br> transactionDateTime = fecPago <br> loanId = request.loanId <br> installmentReference = Transaccion.idAutorizacion  <br> paymentAmount = request.paymentAmount

                API->>event: Envía envento al eventBridge API Idempotencia 
                Note right of API: Mensaje: <br> Correlation-Id: header.Correlation-Id <br> Caller-Service: lambda.caller-service <br> detail-type: "provider.response" <br> request: {request} <br> Transaccion: success 

                API->>Consumidor: Response Exitoso
                Note left of API: HTTP 200: Response Body 

            else If success != false 

                API->>event: Envía envento al eventBridge API Idempotencia 
                Note right of API: Mensaje: <br> Correlation-Id: header.Correlation-Id <br> Caller-Service: lambda.caller-service <br> detail-type: "provider.response" <br> request: {request} <br> Transaccion: TimeOut

                API->> Errors: Mapear código de error

                Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado

                API->> Consumidor: Retorna error
                Note left of API: HTTP 422 + Wrapper.mensajeError

            end
        
        end

    end

    Note over Consumidor, Errors: Flujo Alternativo - Error
    activate API
    alt Exception occurs
        note over Errors: Error Library Handler
        activate Errors
            API->> Errors: Mapear código de error
            Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado
        deactivate Errors
        activate Consumidor
            API-->> Consumidor: Retorna error
        deactivate Consumidor
        Note over Consumidor,Errors: Diagrama guía de manejo de errores <br> http://bit.ly/4rpKVIU
    end
    deactivate API